content: 1. The bounty campaign will be managed by   bitcoinking2. All participants must join Bounty telegram group3. Refrain from promoting talking about bounty programs in project chat groups.An immediate ban from company chat groups. Please ask your bounty-related questions in our bounty group.4. Please note that any offensive or inappropriate behavior may result in your being rejected.5. Using multiple accounts, cheating and spamming will get you disqualified from the bounty program and all your accounts will be permanently banned.6. Red Trust accounts will not be accepted in any way.7. All participants must submit their weekly reports to this bounty thread. For every week, you need to create new report. Anyone submitting the same work twice will be rejected.8. All participants must send the Proof of Authentication post to join the bounty program.      Note: the rewards distribution guarantee by project team.Proof Of Registration Format (All participants must send 1 time):Code:#PROOF OF REGISTRATIONForum Username:Forum Profile Link:Telegram Username:Participated Campaigns:BEP-20 Wallet Address:Weekly report:Code:Week:Bitcointalk Username:Telegram Username:[b]Twitter Campaign[/b]Twitter Profile Url:Spreadsheet No:Retweets/Tweets Url:1. …2. …3. …4. …5. …Tweet url:1. ...2. ...[b]Telegram Campaign[/b]Telegram Username:Spreadsheet No:Telegram posts Url:1. …2. …3. …4. …5. …                              Twitter         50%                             Telegram      50%                                      Week 1: 20/09_26/09                                      Week 2: 27/09_03/10                                      Week 3: 04/10_10/10                                       Week 4: 11/10_17/10                   Rewards:1. Have more than 501 followers: 1 stake/week2. Have more than 1501 followers: 2 stakes/week3. Have more than 5001 followers: 3 stakes/week4. Have more than 10,001 followers: 4 stakes/week                     Rules:  1. Every participant must follow his Twitter Page.2. Twitter accounts must have a minimum of 501 followers.3. Participants have to make new 2 tweets and retweet 5 per week (maximum 1 retweet/day).4. Time gap between 2 retweets/tweets needs to be 10 hours5. Participants must use #Gangster #BSC  #cryptocurrency #blockchain #Crypto #GTOs hashtags in every retweet or tweet.                                    How to join                 Join Bounty And GTOs Telegram group                                 Join here                               Spreadsheet                                              Rewards:                                        5 stakes/week                                              Rules:1. Write at least 5 constructive messages in other crypto-related telegram groups.Posts/messages must be constructive, useful and in a way which will not be considered as spamming.2. Deleted messages will not be counted.3. Report your telegram message links weekly. Please obey the report dates and format.4. You must stay in the telegram group until the end of the campaign to receive your stakes.                                 How to join                 Join Bounty And GTOs Telegram group                                  Join here                                 Spreadsheet
